{"tid":825292,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"「突發」VTC明天復課","createTime":"2018-09-17T12:56:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-17T15:30:44.000Z","uid":165934,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"ea3c62704f776ee61bb7bf4067a35821569691e4","tid":825292,"uid":165934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T12:56:24.000Z","msg":"職業訓練局(VTC)大部分院校明天復課<br />\n<br />\nVTC大部分院校明天（2018年9月18日）復課，除機構成員展亮技能發展中心明天繼續停課。<br />\n<br />\n隨著颱風遠離本港，VTC各院校已積極跟進清理工作，在評估相關情況後，除展亮技能發展中心外，其他院校將於明天如常上課。<br />\n<br />\n明天復課的機構成員或院校包括香港高等教育科技學院（THEi）、高峰進修學院（PEAK）、才晉高等教育學院（SHAPE）、香港專業教育學院（IVE）、香港知專設計學院（HKDI）、酒店及旅遊學院（HTI）、中華廚藝學院（CCI）、國際廚藝學院（ICI）、海事訓練學院（MSTI）、青年學院[包括青年學院(國際)]、工商資訊學院(SBI) 丶卓越培訓發展中心（Pro-Act by VTC）及匯縱專業發展中心（IVDC)。<br />\n<br />\n若同學或員工因交通狀況及安全考量等未能準時回校，院校應體諒個別受影響情況，作彈性處理。"},{"pid":"f976aefadc5cfb65b394158c47867145067d0462","tid":825292,"uid":205856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T12:57:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a658806bc84acb514e8c62e92cdb44b46b448cd7","tid":825292,"uid":120070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T12:59:53.000Z","msg":"好波呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  係柒啲架啦 vtc"},{"pid":"13bc451a86919c181787117d54a708fde3d23917","tid":825292,"uid":206382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T13:01:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1505c32887b4bfddec249051aff2b513ff2039e2","tid":825292,"uid":26952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T13:02:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/17/210236_445d2c4806ec9d14a6ba33a26996b011.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F17%2F210236_445d2c4806ec9d14a6ba33a26996b011.png&h=1c91bd0f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gi